data.description: This spacious 4 bed, 2.5 bath brick home, on a large corner lot, is 2,685 sq ft of perfectly designed living space. From the gourmet kitchen that boasts a large island with seating, storage, and abundance of counter space, walk in pantry, open concept dining and family room complete with a wood-burning fireplace to the mudroom with a storage bench, and generous laundry room all designed with a family in mind.  The gorgeous owner suite features a dual sink vanity, garden tub, separate shower, and a HUGE walk-in closet. A powder room and home office round out the main floor. Upstairs, a multi-purpose loft makes a perfect second family room with three additional bedrooms all with walk in closets and a shared dual sink bathroom. A welcoming front porch and large covered patio complete the home. This is a one owner, Riverside home in a fantastic neighborhood that we know you will fall in love with.
